msgctxt " 	 		73	148	75"
msgid "Isn't this your pen, ma'am?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	70	238	168"
msgid "Are you sure? This looks\\r\n"
"really expensive!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	129	385	256"
msgid "It doesn't just <Italic>look</Italic> expensive.\\r\n"
"It is. Take good care of it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	474	414"
msgid "I'll treasure it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	556	496"
msgid "That fountain pen has a story."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	164	740	576"
msgid "It was a gift back when my debut was\\r\n"
"announced, from someone very dear to me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	78	849	771"
msgid "It's been my good luck charm ever since."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	133	1001	868"
msgid "I even brought it on stage with me\\r\n"
"the night of my debut, hidden behind the mic."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	127	1153	1026"
msgid "Wow. You must have been really nervous, huh?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	85	1285	1200"
msgid "That night was child's play in hindsight."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	84	1381	1297"
msgid "It's what comes after your debut\\r\n"
"that really matters."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	117	1545	1428"
msgid "In my case, my whole life\\r\n"
"got turned upside down."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	1626	1566"
msgid "What happened?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	123	1817	1694"
msgid "Well, when I debuted at eighteen..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　		60	1896	1836"
msgid "I was already married."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	79	2005	1926"
msgid "To the man who gave me that pen."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	134	2166	2032"
msgid "Of course, I kept it a secret from\\r\n"
"my agency, and the world."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	153	2348	2195"
msgid "I was already hiding both my troubled\\r\n"
"upbringing and my Korean ancestry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	155	2504	2349"
msgid "My marriage was just one more\\r\n"
"needle in the haystack."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	60	2600	2540"
msgid "It went surprisingly fine for a time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	2691	2631"
msgid "But one day..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	95	2815	2720"
msgid "I realized I had gotten pregnant."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	2941	2881"
msgid "I got rid of it right away."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	73	3033	2960"
msgid "I didn't hesitate much at the time."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	187	3237	3050"
msgid "I was still so young. I thought it was just\\r\n"
"a sacrifice I had to make as an idol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	67	3335	3268"
msgid "I didn't tell my husband until afterward."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	134	3504	3370"
msgid "He had never hit me before that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	143	3778	3635"
msgid "And then... he left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	116	3935	3819"
msgid "Said he'd just be holding me\\r\n"
"back from my dream if he stayed."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	99	4103	4004"
msgid "I accepted it as another necessary sacrifice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	162	4314	4152"
msgid "But not long after, my agency found out\\r\n"
"that I had been secretly married."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	89	4416	4327"
msgid "They were hesitant to promote me after that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	191	4569	4455"
msgid "My scandal was a ticking timebomb waiting to blow."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	76	4646	4570"
msgid "So naturally they didn't want to invest in me."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	107	4781	4674"
msgid "Event after event was scratched off my schedule."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	148	4960	4812"
msgid "Even a massive concert at the Japan Dome.\\r\n"
"It would've been spectacular."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	169	5189	5020"
msgid "You were such a big deal, ma'am.\\r\n"
"I had no idea."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	82	5375	5293"
msgid "That concert was my dream."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	193	5605	5412"
msgid "I was going to show the world. Show the family\\r\n"
"that abandoned me... that I'd finally made it."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	76	5725	5649"
msgid "A crowd of 55,000."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	117	5949	5832"
msgid "Not bad for a girl who wasn't\\r\n"
"even loved by her own parents."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	144	6128	5984"
msgid "I thought maybe, just maybe my ex\\r\n"
"would come to cheer me on, too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	60	6201	6141"
msgid "Silly, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	131	6404	6273"
msgid "But it never came to be.\\r\n"
"My agency made sure of that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	114	6538	6424"
msgid "Forget the concert. I could\\r\n"
"barely even book a gig after that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	111	6680	6569"
msgid "Until finally, even the smallest leads dried up."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	OK	190	6921	6731"
msgid "Learning I could no longer bear children\\r\n"
"was the final insult. I was broken."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	7041	6981"
msgid "I'm so sorry."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	132	7286	7151"
msgid "I wasn't sure if I'd ever make amends\\r\n"
"for what I sacrificed to become a star."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	175	7505	7330"
msgid "Thinking back on it, maybe that's why\\r\n"
"I wanted to help develop a successful idol."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	167	7713	7546"
msgid "Perhaps I'm just struggling to\\r\n"
"find some form of redemption."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	125	7872	7747"
msgid "Either way, this is all I have left."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	77	8044	7967"
msgid "Sorry to have dragged you into this."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	176	8239	8063"
msgid "Don't say that! I'll work hard,\\r\n"
"for you and me both, ma'am."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	8386	8326"
msgid "Thank you, Haruka."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	　	60	8463	8403"
msgid "And you know..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt " 	　	分	149	8622	8473"
msgid "Thanks to you, I may have already\\r\n"
"gotten back a bit of what I lost."
msgstr ""

